MATCH (n:Country) RETURN n AS node: This query returns all nodes with the label "Country".
MATCH (n:BusinessPartner) RETURN n AS no: This query returns all nodes with the label BusinessPartner.
MATCH (n:Supplier) RETURN n AS node: This query returns all nodes with the label "Supplier".
MATCH (n:Country) WHERE n.country_risk >: This query returns all countries with a country risk greater than 4.976.
MATCH (n:BusinessPartner) WHERE n.agg_sc: This query returns all BusinessPartner nodes with an agg_score greater than 0.051.
MATCH (n:Supplier) WHERE n.supply_networ: This query returns all Supplier nodes with a supply_network_triangles_norm value greater than 0.0.
MATCH (n:Country)-[r]->(m:) RETURN *: This query matches all nodes labeled as Country and any relationships connected to them, and returns all results.
MATCH (n:BusinessPartner)-[r]->(m:) RETU: This query matches all nodes labeled as BusinessPartner and any relationships they have to other nodes.
MATCH (n:Supplier)-[r]->(m:) RETURN *: This query matches all nodes labeled as Supplier and all relationships connected to them.
MATCH (n:Country)-[r]->(m:) RETURN n,m: This query matches all nodes labeled as Country and any relationships connected to them, and returns the nodes and relationships.
